reviews.review_text: Best Fire on the Mountain ever? Surely this has to be close to the best Fire in quite some time.  Please, someone turn me on to another that is equal in beauty.
Best Fire? Although this Fire rips phonebooks in half with ease, there HAS to be one just a little bit better.  Anyone?  Anyone?
Best Fire? Boy, it's tough to surpass this gem, but the Richmond, VA 5/25/77 Scarlet>Fire gives it a run for it's money... Just my humble opinion.

other good Fires 9/2/78, 5/11/80, 9/12/81 and 12/26/81 (never later)

Salt Lake, Portland, Vegas, Tempe, Berkeley, Indi. and Oakland are all good especially the four Dews. lol
